* 02_show_context_menu.patch:
  patch from ubuntu, modified to hide some entries on the contextual menu

* 12_restricted_menu_on_desktop.patch
  use the restricted menu directory to display application icons on the menu

* 14_less_scary_tooltips.patch
  only show the file name in tooltip, or name + comment if the icon is a
  launcher

* 15_simpler_settings.patch
  when CustomizeBehavior is not allowed, hide the main checkbox and the
  behavior tab in the settings dialog

* 16_restore_parent_cursor.patch
  use the parent cursor instead of forcing GDK_LEFT_PTR (fixes startup
  notification)
